    have to correspond to real personal information.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Password</strong>: Stored using secure hashing. We never
    store plaintext passwords.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Session cookies</strong>: Used to keep you logged in. No
    tracking cookies or advertising cookies.
  </li>
</ul>

<h3>3. How We Use Data</h3>
<ul>
  <li>To authenticate you and allow you to manage your plugins.</li>
  <li>To display plugin analytics you have access to.</li>
  <li>To protect the service from abuse (e.g., rate limiting).</li>
</ul>

